ia you can find to argue about in my posts until I get tired and let you have the last post? Actually, <span></span>I am gonna do that now. Adios.</span></div><p>Message Edited by Brutul_PB on <span class="date_text">04-17-2006</span><span class="time_text">01:49 PM</span></p>	
